og og fors\u00f8k p\u00e5 p\u00e5virkning m\u00e5 ha g\u00e5tt galt. Det har rettere sagt ikke v\u00e6rt gjort noen slike fors\u00f8k. Vi m\u00e5 heller pr\u00f8ve mykere tiltak f\u00f8r man umyndiggj\u00f8r foreldre.", "\u00c5 la hijaben ligge hjemme kan v\u00e6re en diskusjon i skolen, mellom foreldre og i moskeene. Ikke et forbud.", "Mihriban@live.no"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|meninger"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "2504cd6567f9595b70b828f80163d02c0778f92144c5f8343b21c1755775ac38"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-10-06T10:25:03.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Etter at Hadia Tajik, Arbeiderpartiets nestleder, uttalte at hun vil forby hijab i barneskolen fordi det seksualiserer barn, har det v\u00e6rt mange sterke reaksjoner."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/meninger/article11898644.ece/euy1de/ALTERNATES/w980-default/hijab21.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d27c91af8aabc12bd506de7befa641891d5c3352.jpg?58d44bed"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Barn beh\u00f8ver ikke hijab -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "d27c91af8aabc12bd506de7befa641891d5c3352"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "meninger"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["hijab", "religi\u00f8se plagg", "barn"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["kolstad", "arbeiderpartiets"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "norge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "hadia tajik"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss/meninger", "pluss"]}, {"field": "og-image